16281701[=]ustv[=]3460484[=]2010-12-09 21:45:15[=]Notes of the Big C S01E04&05[=]Notes of the Big C S01E04&05 1.cash out one's account 取光存款。 Cathy 因为cancer要提前取出所有的退休金，意味着她要forfeit(放弃) half of her money. 2.It is not recommended. 不推荐这样做。 瞧瞧，地道的原来是这么说的，换成我，就说we don't recommend that...,就成中式英文了，学一个， ^_^ 3.save for a rainy day 未雨绸缪 4. You are not allowed to be the popular parent. 谁许你做白脸，让我做黑脸啦？ 做父母的都有一个白脸，一个黑脸，白脸的就叫the popular parent吧，我自己翻译的，哈哈。 5.do impulsive things 做事冲动，临时起兴 6. unload the car 卸下车上的东西 7. male logic/female logic 男性逻辑/女性逻辑 男性来自火星，女性来自金星的嘛，Men Are from Mars, Women Are from Venus 8.behind the scene 幕后 9.women need attention, if even they act like they don't, if even they say they don't want you to make a fuss about valentine's day or their birthdays, deep down, they wish you would. 女人喜欢被关注，即使她表现得她并不在乎，即使她说不必在情人节或是生日的时候大张旗鼓，但内心深处，她还是希望你去给她惊喜。 Cathy给Adam的性启蒙教育，I will every mother would do the same thing to her son, so there would be fewer heartbroken girls. 10. all the dreams get crushed by reality 现实粉碎梦想 11.nothing I can't handle 一切在我掌握之中 12.if any consolation,... 要讲些安慰人的话之前可以这么用 13.if memory serves... 如果没记错的话...，还可以说if memory didn't fail me... That's all for today...
