11599180[=]ustv[=]noheartnolove[=]2010-05-27 09:43:28[=]标题：To remember,to let go and move on.------LOST ----转[=]It's time to leave. Oceanic 815 Christian Shephard Desmond to Kate:No one can tell you why you are here.I'm not talking about church, about jere. Hugo to Sayid:That's your choice Juliet helps Sun and Jin remember everthing, they are ready to leave. Jack to Desmond : What happened, happened. To remember, there are rules. Hugo to Sayid: You can't let other people tell you what you are,you have to decide that for yourself. Hugo helps Sayid and Shannon remember everthing, they are ready to leave. Daniel and Charlotte are not ready to leave, so they can't remember. Kate helps Claire and Charlie remember everthing, they are ready to leave. Jack and Lock , fight. Lock died. Kate to Jack when she will leave:I love you Jack answered: I love you,too. Jack helps Lock remember everthing, he is ready to leave Lock to Jack: You don't have a son.I hope that somebody dose for you what you just did for me. Sawyer and Juliet remember everthing, they are ready to leave. Kate to Jack when Concert was over:I missed you so much. Jack to Hugo:Drink this...Now you are like me. Desmond to Jack: The light.I put it out.It didn't work.I thought I'd leave this place,but I still here. Jack to Desmond: I 'll see you in another life,brother. Outside the Church：Ben and Lock Ben:I'm very sorry for what I did to you, John. I was selfish and jealous.I wanted everything you had. Lock:What did I have? Ben:You w'ere special,John, and I wasn't. Lock:Well, if it helps, Ben,I forgive you. Ben:Thank you.John.That dose help. It matters more than I can say. Lock:What are you gonna do now? Ben:I have some things that I still need to work out. I think I'll stay here a while. Outside the Church：Jack and Kate Jack: Where are you going? Kate: Inside. I'll be waiting for you there...once you're ready. Jack: Ready for what? Kate: To Leave! A room in Church: Jack and his dad(Christian Shephard) Dad: Hi,kiddo. Jack:Dad? Dad: Hello Jack. Jack: I don't understand.You died! Dad:Yeah. Yes! I diid. Jack:Then how are you here right now? Dad: How are you here? Jack:I died, too?! Dad:It's okay, son. Jack:I love you,dad. Dad: I love you, too,son. Jack:Are you... Are you real? Dad: I sure hope so.Yeah, I'm real. You're real.Everything that's ever happened to you is real.All those people in the church, they are all real,too. Jack: They are all...They're all dead? Dad: Everyone dies sometime,kiddo. Some of them before you, some...long after you. Jack:But why are they all here now? Dad: well, there's no "now" here. Jack: Where are we,dad? Dad: This is a place that you...that you all made together so that you could find one another.The most important part of your life was the time that you spent with these people. That's why all of you are here.Nobody dose it alone,Jack. You needed all of them, and they needed you. Jack: For what? Dad: To remember.And to...let go. Jack: Kate, she said we were leaving. Dad:Not leave.No. Moving on! Jack:Where are we going? Dad:Let's go find out. On the island, Jack closed his eyes. Dog Vincent was the only one who was here with him. The End OF LOST. 以上是我记下的，不想有太多的情节说明，到现在，情节已经不重要了，what happened,happened。之前是无法接受结局，那么美好的世界，怎么一下子成了be made together so that they could find one another.现在，我学会接受，换一个角度 Everyone dies some time,some before you, some long after you.这已说明一切。人早晚是要死的，这个闪旁的美好世界没有“now”，只为大家聚到一起to remember、to let go and move on. Ben最终没有进教堂，和Ilana一样没有准备好，他还纠结于生前因为自私所作的一切，既然Lock都可以放手了，Ben也应该放手。 一直寄希望于好的结局，Oceanic815 never crashed. 不过JJ的结局，现在想想，也不错。学会接受。大家在天堂永远快乐的生活才是真正的大团圆结局。看着他们一对一对的被唤起生前的记忆，然后是拥抱，lost走温情路线又何尝不可？ Kate和Jack这对暧昧的恋人，在此生最后离别的时候终于说出了“I Love You ”。为了等这句，我整整看了这么多年。多年的疑问也终于解答，Kate还是最爱Jack。当Kate说出那句话时，Jack的表情有些复杂，他肯定也是刚刚确定Kate的真心。那句“I missed you so much”足以证明了生死把他两分开了有多久。 结果不重要，过程才是。每一年的那几个月，那几个月的每一周，每一周的某一天，都是伴着那刺激、神秘的剧情度过的。以后都不会有了。 To remember, to let go and move on.
