12913381[=]ustv[=]43871241[=]2010-07-24 22:55:31[=]女性心目中十件最浪漫的事[=]　　心理学教授Richard在一项全球范围内的调查发现，英国人和他们邻国人相比缺乏浪漫细胞。其实，想要博得女性的欢心，不必花太 多钱。最重要的是真心实意。 Psychologist Professor Richard Wiseman claims that British men are some of the least romantic in the world following a study he conducted of 6,500 men and women all over the world. He found that they are less likely to pay compliments, be inspired to write love poetry or take their loved ones away for surprise holidays than their foreign counterparts, instead believing sexy lingerie and expensive gifts are the way to a woman's heart. The following are the ten best ways to woo her: 1. Cover her eyes and lead her to a lovely surprise 遮住她的双眼，然后引导她看到一个惊喜 2. Whisk her away somewhere exciting for the weekend 带她去一个好玩的地方度周末 3. Write a song or poem about her 写一首关于她的歌或诗 4. Tell her that she is the most wonderful woman you have ever met 跟她说，她是你遇见过的最好的女人 5. Run her a relaxing bath after she has had a bad day at work 在她辛苦了一天下班回到家后，把浴缸放满热水，让她洗个澡放松一下 6. Use her photo to make a book-liked birthday present to her(Don't ask me what is it,Google it,you'll find) 用她的照片做一本“像书一样的本子”作为生日礼物送给她。 点击查看：http://item.taobao.com/item.htm?id=4501958869 7. Wake her up with breakfast in bed 把早餐端到床前，然后唤醒她 8. Offer her a coat when she is cold 当她感觉冷的时候，替她披上外套 9. Send her a bouquet of flowers, or a box of chocolates at work 在她上班的时候，给她快递去一束鲜花或者一盒巧克力 10. Make her a compilation of her favourite music 把她最喜欢的音乐编辑成一张专辑
